name: Carnival
description:
"The House of Mirrors is starting to crumble - as is everything else around it. This once magical realm of dazzling lights and enticing reflections, where anything was possible. Where imagination could create images out of infinite fragments, now only exists in our memories and dreams" - Sykcolo / AI

Carnival by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of fur from a what looked like a discarded fairground prize. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
